node.text:
Do you keep getting cheated on? Feeling used? Heart broken every time? Can’t keep them interested? Failed relationships? ⁣
⁣
The problem is you! YOU keep picking the same “type” ⁣
⁣
Look, I’m honest with everyone I coach. Trust me, this is a normal thing we all deal with. But once you realize this, you can change who you date easily with being more open minded to different types. ⁣
⁣
What is your “type” that you haven’t had much luck with so far??? Be honest lol 😆

node.text:
Beware of the scammers these days... honestly, it’s very hard these day’s to date online because there is so many scams. 
Red flags- -if they have barely any pics up, no tags from friends.. -super super sexy woman and claims it’s her private page... -won’t Skype or FaceTime you. Makes excuses -claims very sad stories to get money from you.. - remember to reverse photo lookup on google to make sure pics are authentic!!!! Usually they are stolen. I have sooo many scammers steal my images as well, it’s awful.
